description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Core Strength' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Fire up your core with Peter in this workout featuring four core-focused exercises. Explicit lyrics....
